div.p: Memory-resident page cache with O(1) lookup, LRU eviction, and pin-based protection
Purpose: O(1) lookup by page_id Type: Hash table with chaining
Head: Most recently used Tail: Least recently used (eviction victim)

ol.li: If hit: pin++, move to LRU head
If miss: find free/evict, load from disk
If dirty: write to disk first

div.p: page_id: -1 (empty) pin_count: 0 is_dirty: false data[0..4095]: free
